  Someone's in a <strong>good mood</strong> today! That's great!
</h3>
<p class="emotion-title">Savour this moment. Feeling joy has many posoitive effects for your mind and body. It boosts your immune system, fights long term stress and even promotes an overall healthier lifestyle.</p>
